2005年，当[[史提夫·喬布斯|史提夫·喬布斯]]開始筹备iPhone时，他可以選擇「把Mac縮小，這將會是工程學上一個史詩般的壯舉，或是把iPod擴大」。喬布斯贊成前者的做法，但仍然讓[[麥金塔|麥金塔]]及[[iPod|iPod]]團隊（分別由[[史考特·福斯托|史考特·福斯托]]及[[托尼·法戴爾|托尼·法戴爾]]所領導）在公司內部互相競爭，最終由麥金塔團隊創建的iPhone OS勝出。这个决定成功使iPhone成为了第三方开发者乐于参与的平台，因为他们花费很小的学习成本就能为建立于著名系统Mac上的iPhone OS创造程序。福斯托还负责创建用于开发iPhone应用程序的[[软件开发工具包|软件开发工具包]]，以及设在[[iTunes|iTunes]]内的[[App_Store_(iOS/iPadOS)|App Store]]<ref>{{Cite web |title=Scott Forstall, the Sorcerer's Apprentice at Apple |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2011-10-12/scott-forstall-the-sorcerers-apprentice-at-apple |accessdate=2017-04-01 |date=2011-10-14 |publisher=[[Bloomberg_L.P.|Bloomberg L.P.]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170407032342/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2011-10-12/scott-forstall-the-sorcerers-apprentice-at-apple |archivedate=2017-04-07 |first1=Adam |last1=Satariano |first2=Peter |last2=Burrows |first3=Brad |last3=Stone |website=[[Bloomberg_Businessweek|Bloomberg Businessweek]] |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=Scott Forstall's Personality, Origins of iOS, and Lost iPhone 4 Prototype |url=https://www.macrumors.com/2011/10/13/scott-forstalls-personality-origins-of-ios-and-lost-iphone-4-prototype/ |accessdate=2017-04-01 |date=2011-10-12 |last=Kim |first=Arnold |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170402081118/https://www.macrumors.com/2011/10/13/scott-forstalls-personality-origins-of-ios-and-lost-iphone-4-prototype/ |archivedate=2017-04-02 |website=[[MacRumors|MacRumors]] |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

