-09 |last=Wright |first=Mic |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170401232647/https://thenextweb.com/apple/2015/09/09/genius-annotated-with-genius/ |archivedate=2017-04-01 |website=The Next Web |deadurl=no }}</ref>」，然而在iPhone發布時，其操作系统被重新命名為「iPhone OS」<ref>{{Cite web |title=iOS: A visual history |url=https://www.theverge.com/2011/12/13/2612736/ios-history-iphone-ipad |accessdate=2017-04-01 |date=2013-09-16 |publisher=[[Vox_Media|Vox Media]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170412015548/http://www.theverge.com/2011/12/13/2612736/ios-history-iphone-ipad |archivedate=2017-04-12 |website=[[The_Verge|The Verge]] |deadurl=no }}</ref>。最初，本機應用程式並不支援第三方的應用程式。喬布斯的理由是，開發者可以透過[[Safari|Safari網頁瀏覽器]]構建[[网络应用程序|Web應用程序]]，「就像iPhone上的原生應用程式一般<ref>{{Cite web |title=Apple Launches iPhone Web Apps Directory |url=http://www.informationweek.com/apple-launches-iphone-web-apps-directory/d/d-id/1060220 |accessdate=2017-04-01 |date=2007-10-11 |last=Gonsalves |first=Antone |publisher=[[UBM_plc|UBM plc]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170220092434/http://www.informationweek.com/apple-launches-iphone-web-apps-directory/d/d-id/1060220 |archivedate=2017-02-20 |website=[[InformationWeek|InformationWeek]] |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=Jobs’ original vision for the iPhone: No third-party native apps |url=https://9to5mac.com/2011/10/21/jobs-original-vision-for-the-iphone-no-third-party-native-apps/ |accessdate=2017-04-01 |date=2011-10-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170401233112/https://9to5mac.com/2011/10/21/jobs-original-vision-for-the-iphone-no-third-party-native-apps/ |archivedate=2017-04-01 |website=9to5Mac |deadurl=no }}</ref>」。2007年10月，Apple宣布正在開發一個[[軟體開發套件|軟體開發套件]]，並且他們計劃在次年2月把它提供給開發人員<ref>{{Cite web |title=Apple: "we plan to have an iPhone SDK in developers' hands in February" |url=https://www.engadget.com/2007/10/17/apple-we-plan-to-have-an-iphone-sdk-in-developers-hands-in-fe/ |accessdate=2017-04-01 |date=2007-10-17 |last=Fletcher |first=Ni